Definition: a public relations person who tries to forestall negative publicity by publicizing a favorable interpretation of the words or actions of a company or political party or famous person
Example: his title is Director of Communications but he is just a spin doctor
Synonyms: spinmeister, public_relations_person, a, public, relations, person, who, tries, to, forestall, negative, publicity, by, publicizing, favorable, interpretation, of, the, words, or, actions, company, political, party, famous, his, title, is, Director, Communications, but, he, just, spin, doctor
Category: noun.person
